    "body" : "<p>I needed same thing and this solution work fine, hope it can help someone also</p>\n\n<pre><code>Enumeration[] array = Enumeration.values();\nList&lt;Enumeration&gt; list = Arrays.asList(array);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>then you can get the .name() of your enumeration.</p>\n"
