  "title" : "Convert Enumeration to a Set/List",
  "body" : "<p>Is there some one-liner bridge method to dump a given <em>Enumeration</em> to <code>java.util.List</code> or <code>java.util.Set</code>?</p>\n<p>Something built-in like <code>Arrays.asList()</code> or <code>Collection.toArray()</code> should exist somewhere, but I'm unable to find that in my IntelliJ debugger's evaluator window (and Google/SO results, too).</p>\n"
